
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Fode-DevOps | Ingénieur Cloud & DevOps</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@400;600;700&family=Source+Code+Pro:wght@300;400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #2A3F54;
            --secondary: #1ABB9C;
            --accent: #3498DB;
            --dark: #1A2A3A;
            --light: #F7F9FC;
            --text: #34495E;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--light);
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: var(--text);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--dark));
            color: white;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .header::after {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 3px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--secondary), var(--accent));
        }
        
        .avatar {
            width: 120px;
            height: 120px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 4px solid var(--secondary);
            margin: 0 auto 20px;
            background: #eee;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 50px;
            color: var(--primary);
            transition: transform 0.3s;
        }
        
        .avatar:hover {
            transform: rotate(10deg);
        }
        
        h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 2.5em;
            letter-spacing: -1px;
        }
        
        .tagline {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            opacity: 0.9;
            margin: 10px 0 0;
        }
        
        .section {
            padding: 40px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
        }
        
        .section-title {
            color: var(--primary);
            margin-top: 0;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            position: relative;
            padding-left: 15px;
        }
        
        .section-title::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            top: 5px;
            height: 80%;
            width: 4px;
            background: var(--secondary);
            border-radius: 2px;
        }
        
        .section-title i {
            margin-right: 15px;
            color: var(--secondary);
        }
        
        .skills-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        
        .skill-card {
            background: var(--light);
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 20px;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            border-left: 4px solid var(--secondary);
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }
        
        .skill-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        
        .skill-title {
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 0 0 10px;
            color: var(--primary);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }
        
        .skill-desc {
            font-size: 0.9em;
            color: #7F8C8D;
        }
        
        .project {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            background: var(--light);
        }
        
        .project:hover {
            transform: translateX(5px);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }
        
        .project-title {
            font-size: 1.3em;
            color: var(--primary);
            margin: 0 0 10px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }
        
        .project-tech {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 10px;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
        
        .tech-tag {
            background: rgba(42, 63, 84, 0.1);
            padding: 5px 12px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 0.8em;
            color: var(--primary);
            border: 1px solid rgba(42, 63, 84, 0.2);
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }
        
        .tech-tag:hover {
            background: var(--secondary);
            color: white;
            border-color: var(--secondary);
        }
        
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px;
            background: var(--primary);
            color: white;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .footer::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 3px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--secondary), var(--accent));
        }
        
        .social-links {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        
        .social-links a {
            color: white;
            font-size: 1.5em;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        
        .social-links a:hover {
            color: var(--secondary);
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            transform: translateY(-3px);
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .skills-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
            
            .section {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }
            
            h1 {
                font-size: 2em;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="avatar">
                <i class="fas fa-server"></i>
            </div>
            <h1>Fode-DevOps</h1>
            <p class="tagline">Expert en Infrastructure Cloud & Automatisation</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="section">
            <h2 class="section-title"><i class="fas fa-user-tie"></i> Profil Professionnel</h2>
            <p>Ingénieur DevOps avec plus de 5 ans d'expérience dans la conception, la mise en œuvre et la maintenance d'infrastructures cloud évolutives sur AWS. Spécialisé en Infrastructure as Code (Terraform, Ansible) et pipelines CI/CD. Passionné par l'automatisation, la sécurité et l'optimisation des coûts cloud.</p>
            
            <div class="skills-grid">
                <div class="skill-card">
                    <h3 class="skill-title"><i class="fas fa-code-branch"></i> Maîtrise de Terraform</h3>
                    <p class="skill-desc">Conception et implémentation de code Terraform modulaire et réutilisable pour des environnements AWS multi-comptes avec workspaces et état distant.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="skill-card">
                    <h3 class="skill-title"><i class="fas fa-robot"></i> Automatisation Ansible</h3>
                    <p class="skill-desc">Gestion de configuration à grande échelle avec inventaires dynamiques, modules personnalisés et playbooks basés sur des rôles.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="skill-card">
                    <h3 class="skill-title"><i class="fab fa-aws"></i> Architecture AWS</h3>
                    <p class="skill-desc">Solutions bien architecturées utilisant EC2, ECS, Lambda, RDS, S3, VPC et les services de sécurité.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="skill-card">
                    <h3 class="skill-title"><i class="fas fa-tasks"></i> Pipelines CI/CD</h3>
                    <p class="skill-desc">Mise en œuvre de GitHub Actions, Jenkins et CodePipeline avec tests d'infrastructure.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="section">
            <h2 class="section-title"><i class="fas fa-project-diagram"></i> Projets Récents</h2>
            
            <div class="project">
                <h3 class="project-title"><i class="fas fa-kubernetes"></i> Plateforme Kubernetes Multi-Cloud</h3>
                <p>Conception et implémentation d'un cluster EKS de qualité production avec Terraform, incluant le réseau VPC, les groupes de nœuds et l'intégration avec les services AWS (ALB, RDS, ElastiCache).</p>
                <div class="project-tech">
                    <span class="tech-tag">Terraform</span>
                    <span class="tech-tag">AWS EKS</span>
                    <span class="tech-tag">Helm</span>
                    <span class="tech-tag">Ansible</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="project">
                <h3 class="project-title"><i class="fas fa-layer-group"></i> Framework d'Infrastructure as Code</h3>
                <p>Développement d'un framework Terraform réutilisable pour le déploiement rapide d'environnements AWS standardisés à travers plusieurs unités commerciales avec des contrôles de réseau et de sécurité centralisés.</p>
                <div class="project-tech">
                    <span class="tech-tag">Modules Terraform</span>
                    <span class="tech-tag">AWS Organizations</span>
                    <span class="tech-tag">SCP</span>
                    <span class="tech-tag">Terragrunt</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="project">
                <h3 class="project-title"><i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i> Durcissement Sécurisé Automatisé</h3>
                <p>Création de playbooks Ansible pour la conformité aux benchmarks CIS sur des serveurs Linux et Windows, intégrés avec AWS Systems Manager pour les mises à jour automatiques.</p>
                <div class="project-tech">
                    <span class="tech-tag">Ansible</span>
                    <span class="tech-tag">AWS SSM</span>
                    <span class="tech-tag">Benchmarks CIS</span>
                    <span class="tech-tag">Python</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="section">
            <h2 class="section-title"><i class="fas fa-tools"></i> Stack Technique</h2>
            <div class="skills-grid">
                <div class="skill-card">
                    <h3 class="skill-title"><i class="fas fa-cloud"></i> Plateformes Cloud</h3>
                    <p>AWS, GCP, Azure</p>
                </div>
                <div class="skill-card">
                    <h3 class="skill-title"><i class="fas fa-code"></i> Infrastructure as Code</h3>
                    <p>Terraform, Ansible, Pulumi</p>
                </div>
                <div class="skill-card">
                    <h3 class="skill-title"><i class="fas fa-boxes"></i> Conteneurs & Orchestration</h3>
                    <p>Docker, Kubernetes, ECS, EKS</p>
                </div>
                <div class="skill-card">
                    <h3 class="skill-title"><i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i> Monitoring & Logging</h3>
                    <p>Prometheus, Grafana, ELK, CloudWatch</p>
                </div>
                <div class="skill-card">
                    <h3 class="skill-title"><i class="fas fa-random"></i> Outils CI/CD</h3>
                    <p>Jenkins, GitHub Actions, ArgoCD</p>
                </div>
                <div class="skill-card">
                    <h3 class="skill-title"><i class="fas fa-terminal"></i> Langages de Script</h3>
                    <p>Bash, Python, PowerShell</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>© 2025 Fode-DevOps | Expert en Infrastructure Cloud</p>
            <div class="social-links">
                <a href="#" title="GitHub"><i class="fab fa-github"></i></a>
                <a href="#" title="LinkedIn"><i class="fab fa-linkedin"></i></a>
                <a href="#" title="Twitter"><i class="fab fa-twitter"></i></a>
                <a href="#" title="Email"><i class="fas fa-envelope"></i></a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>

